OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt's the end of an era for Port Talbot
OL,7,F- and for Graham, too. He has worked
OL,8,Fhere for 42 years and in his spare
OL,9,Ftime has documented the various
OL,10,Fchapters of steel making in his
OL,11,Fhometown over hundreds of years.
OL,13,FWith producer Sofia Lewis, whose
OL,14,Ffather worked in the plant, and camera
OL,15,Foperator Trevor Davies, I filmed on
OL,16,Fsite for the very last time in its
OL,17,Fcurrent configuration.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
