OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt's the hottest day of the year so
OL,7,Ffar, and we are fully kitted out in
OL,8,FPPE: two pairs of trousers, three top
OL,9,Flayers, helmet, long socks, safety
OL,10,Fboots, glasses and gloves.
OL,12,FI find it almost impossible to walk,
OL,13,Fand have extra respect for the 4,000-
OL,14,Fstrong workforce here who put a shift
OL,15,Fin every day.
OL,17,FGraham, like many steelmakers, started
OL,18,Fworking alongside his father. Steel is
OL,19,Fin Graham's blood. He proudly tells us
OL,20,Fhis body is covered in tattoos of the
OL,21,Fworks.
