OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FHe says while he feels privileged to
OL,7,Fhave spent his whole working life
OL,8,Fhere, he will be sorry to go in these
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,FGraham will be made redundant as the
OL,12,FPort Talbot workforce drops from more
OL,13,Fthan 4,000 to 1,500 later this year.
OL,15,FAs this blast furnace era draws to a
OL,16,Fclose, another will begin with the
OL,17,Fswitch to an electric arc furnace.
OL,19,FIt's a fundamental shift in technology
OL,20,Ffrom virgin steelmaking, to producing
OL,21,Fsteel from recycled metal.
