OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FTata says it is greener, it will cut
OL,7,Femissions and it is the future.
OL,9,FBut now is a time for reflection.
OL,11,FWhen Graham started work, there were
OL,12,F18,000 workers in this plant. He says
OL,13,Fnumbers have been dropping ever since.
OL,15,FPutting on a brave face, he says:
OL,16,F"That's progression and you just have
OL,17,Fto accept it."
OL,19,FNot everyone has accepted the speed of
OL,20,Fthe transition here.
