OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FThe unions put forward a proposal for
OL,7,Fa slower transition. They argued to
OL,8,Fkeep one blast furnace open - number
OL,9,F4, which still has nine years of life
OL,10,Fin it - while a new arc is built.
OL,12,FIt would have given the workforce, and
OL,13,Fthe community which depends on the
OL,14,Fplant, a chance to catch their breath
OL,15,Fand retrain.
OL,17,FIt would also have avoided thousands
OL,18,Fof workers entering the local job
OL,19,Fmarket all at the same time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
