OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FHowever, as our guide from Tata for
OL,7,Fthe day explained, it is logistically
OL,8,Fimpossible to keep one blast running
OL,9,Fand build an arc furnace at the same
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FHe said it would take twice as long,
OL,13,Fcost twice as much and the company has
OL,14,Fruled it out.
OL,16,FWe head from the high-tech control
OL,17,Froom, with cameras trained on blast
OL,18,Ffurnaces 4 and 5, to the iron-making
OL,19,Fplant.
