OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FVisually, it's basic and spectacular
OL,7,Flike the best bonfire night fireworks
OL,8,FI've ever seen spewing out of a
OL,9,Fglowing cave.
OL,11,FWe watch Blast Furnace No. 5 being
OL,12,F"tapped off". It's a highly controlled
OL,13,Fand regulated environment but it looks
OL,14,Fincredible.
OL,16,FIron and steel has been made in this
OL,17,Fway at Port Talbot for more than 70
OL,18,Fyears, but its days are now over.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
