OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FWe see the area where the new electric
OL,7,Farc furnace will be built in a
OL,8,F#1.25billion investment over the next
OL,9,Fthree years.
OL,11,FThe company is keen to emphasise that
OL,12,Fsomething radical had to be done.
OL,14,FTata says this plant has been losing a
OL,15,Fmillion pounds a day for years and the
OL,16,Farc will guarantee a future for steel
OL,17,Fhere - just a different one.
OL,19,FSteelmaking is not ending, it's just
OL,20,Fchanging.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
