OL,3,CInside Port Talbot's steelworks as
OL,4,Cblast furnace era draws to a close
OL,6,FIt's the sample lines going down to
OL,7,Fthe laboratory for analysis, he tells
OL,8,Fme. It has been the constant
OL,9,Fsoundtrack to Graham's working life.
OL,11,FA new chapter now awaits him, this
OL,12,Fplant and this town built on steel.
OL,13,FThere's sadness and uncertainty here,
OL,14,Fbut also some hope of what's yet to
OL,15,Fcome.
